    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/424de405dab5d814db387a1e4d5a5816.apng?t=1745491282\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/424de405dab5d814db387a1e4d5a5816.poster.avif?t=1745491282\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=138 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多年来保护王国的神奇之壳已经被粉碎。噩梦般的生物群体现在已经占领了王国，恐吓着其居民。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >净白修道院，几个世纪以来一直守护着王国，无法单独面对这种威胁。他们被迫向伊莱亚斯寻求帮助，他是一个半人半妖的存在，血液中流淌着噩梦之血。他可能是王国唯一的希望。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索王国的土地，与大量的噩梦生物和强大的首领战斗，发现秘密，帮助困境中的居民，阻止即将到来的灾难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/20165c0160f258a7f1a8a89b4d6058ae.poster.avif?t=1745491282\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/20165c0160f258a7f1a8a89b4d6058ae.webm?t=1745491282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/20165c0160f258a7f1a8a89b4d6058ae.mp4?t=1745491282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 发现丰富的王国世界，充满传说和氛围。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 令人惊叹的手绘像素艺术和动画。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 近距离与敌人交战，执行令人印象深刻的连招，躲避攻击，并用各种法术攻击他们。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 遇见王国的居民。其中一些人有传闻可供调查。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 参与具有挑战性和引人入胜的首领战斗，游戏中有超过十几个，包括秘密首领。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 探索王国的世界，充满了隐藏的地方和谜团。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 找到物品、法术和能力，帮助你的旅程。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 使用灵感系统定制您的游戏风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/a3ec7200d15a804aa282e8296a9e2bed.poster.avif?t=1745491282\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/a3ec7200d15a804aa282e8296a9e2bed.webm?t=1745491282\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1154090/extras/a3ec7200d15a804aa282e8296a9e2bed.mp4?t=1745491282\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
